About

Ngành Ấu Nhi (the Seedling Division)’s motto is “Ngoan!”, meaning “well behaved”. This division wears green scarves, representing newly budding rice leaves and the wonder, purity, and innocence of this age group. This division consists of members from ages 7 to 9 years old who comprise of three levels: Levels 1, 2, and 3.
